title: Banana cupcakes with caramel cream
ingredients: ['Cupcakes', '300g self-raising flour', '200g soft brown sugar', '1 teaspoon cinnamon', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '2 eggs', '1 teaspoon vanilla', '180ml milk', '80ml light vegetabe oil', '4 large bananas', 'Caramel cream', '300ml whipping cream, whipped', '1 (397g) tin caramel']
